1
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,440
Xie Lao'er!

2
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:14,560
Yang Gang!

3
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,039
Don't run!

4
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,160
Stop chasing.

5
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:41,000
Brother, are we just going to let him go?

6
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:42,560
Situ.

7
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:43,880
Situ!

8
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,460
Saving him is more important.

9
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,800
You're awake.

10
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,160
I... Why am I here?

11
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,960
You fainted by the roadside.

12
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,639
A stranger brought you here.

13
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,560
I...

14
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:14,520
Slow down.

15
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,320
This...

16
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,000
What did you say?

17
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,079
I fainted by the roadside?

18
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,079
You're covered in mud.

19
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,000
I...

20
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,440
Well...

21
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,079
Where did you go?

22
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,720
I remember going to the union office.

23
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:40,050
I was knocked out as soon as I got out of the car.

24
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:41,410
I sent someone to check.

25
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,040
Someone said they saw a stranger

26
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,370
passing by our factory.

27
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:48,680
It must be Xiao Tianman's people taking revenge on me.

28
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,200
Let's call the police first.

29
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,100
Let them investigate with us.

30
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,880
Why is there so much mud here?

31
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,720
Brother, why aren't you eating?

32
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,280
About last night,

33
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,640
don't mention it to anyone.

34
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,640
Because we had no legitimate reason

35
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,200
to be there. Understand?

36
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:24,200
Isn't it a shame not to mention the hero saving the beauty?

37
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,800
What hero saving the beauty?

38
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,660
Making money is what matters now.

39
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,920
Understand?

40
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,120
Brother Gang.

41
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,720
Xiaofeng.

42
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,440
Come here.

43
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,360
Xiaofeng.

44
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,200
Why did you ask me to come here?

45
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,460
Here, take this money.

46
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,770
Go pay your tuition.

47
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,160
Brother Gang, this...

48
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,770
Do you need my help with something?

49
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,380
No, what are you thinking?

50
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,600
I don't have any other demands.

51
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,530
I just want you to go back to school.

52
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,880
Brother Gang.

53
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,600
I appreciate your kindness.

54
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,920
But I can't take this money.

55
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,160
Why?

56
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,780
Studying always costs money.

57
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,160
You can't help us forever.

58
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,760
This is just our fate.

59
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,320
This is not your fate.

60
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,210
Xiaofeng, listen to me.

61
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,560
Don't worry about anything.

62
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,720
Just go back to school.

63
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,520
Alright.

64
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,440
I'll support you until you finish university.

65
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,840
But where will you get that much money?

66
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,170
Don't worry about that.

67
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,240
Let me tell you,

68
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,650
for the kids in our Dayang Village,

69
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:42,159
school is the only way out.

70
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,960
And those friends you hang out with,

71
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,240
call them all back.

72
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,159
Everyone goes back to school.

73
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:49,240
However much money is needed,

74
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,640
whatever is needed, I'll provide it.

75
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:53,880
Okay?

76
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,920
Just teach him a lesson.

77
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,180
Don't make a big scene.

78
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,720
Okay.

79
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:23,640
No... Boss Xiao, what are you doing?

80
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,370
Do you know why I tied you up?

81
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,960
Do you need a reason, Boss Xiao?

82
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,120
You've got some nerve.

83
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:36,130
Making deals with Gao Shan behind my back.

84
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,320
Talk.

85
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,640
Where did the gold come from?

86
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,440
I saved it up.

87
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:45,120
Boss Xiao, I used to find gold dust when I was mining.

88
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,840
Saved it?

89
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,560
Yeah.

90
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,720
You saved that much?

91
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:51,720
Enough to make deals with Gao Shan?

92
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,040
It's not that much.

93
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,040
Just a little bit.

94
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:57,000
I just needed to pay my kid's tuition.

95
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,780
Check if you don't believe me.

96
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,160
Yang Gang, do you think if I didn't have proof,

97
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,560
I'd come looking for you?

98
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,480
Would I?

99
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,000
Yang Gang.

100
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,440
Why did you go to Gao Shan?

101
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:18,480
Boss Xiao, is there a misunderstanding?

102
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,880
A misunderstanding?

103
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,080
I really went to Gao Shan for the gold.

104
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,560
He buys gold from me.

105
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,160
Just for that?

106
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,560
Of course.

107
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,690
Not telling the truth, are you?

108
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,000
Boss Xiao, I'm telling the truth.

109
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,080
Really.

110
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,920
Everyone knows Section Chief Sun is above you.

111
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,520
And you won't buy my gold.

112
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,280
So I had to go to Gao Shan.

113
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,520
Besides, we're from the same village.

114
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,040
Why did you tie me up?

115
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,000
Untie me, now.

116
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,680
Behave.

117
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,440
Put the gold aside for now.

118
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:53,040
But you went to Gao Shan, didn't you?

119
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,680
About this...

120
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,580
You owe me an explanation.

121
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,090
President Xiao.

122
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,840
No, President Xiao.

123
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:13,490
No, Liao Fei. What are you doing, Liao Fei?

124
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,130
All right, President Xiao.

125
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,500
No... Liao Fei, what exactly do you want?

126
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,640
Drive. Just drive.

127
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:41,120
Are you two Xiao Tianman and Xie Lao'er?

128
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,679
Hello. I am Xiao Tianman.

129
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:47,880
We suspect you are involved in the kidnapping of Situ Hongtang.

130
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,740
Please come with us to assist in the investigation.

131
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,480
Sure. We'll cooperate.

132
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,800
You suspect Yang Gang kidnapped you, don't you?

133
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,760
I'm not sure.

134
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:05,080
But I think I heard his voice.

135
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,450
Those miners are hesitant.

136
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,840
Maybe they took Xiao Tianman's money,

137
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,240
and want to get rid of you.

138
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,640
My jacket smells of sulfur.

139
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,920
I must have been taken to a mine.

140
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,450
That connects the dots.

141
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:29,240
Deliberately causing a mining accident...

142
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,440
It delays the reform and gets rid of you.

143
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,770
They're pretty clever.

144
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,940
Thermometer tube.

145
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,840
They're washing gold ore with mercury.

146
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,160
They just left the tools for stealing ore right here.

147
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,960
Are they really this brazen?

148
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,280
Du Jing,

149
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,780
come over here.

150
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,960
Look at the position of the bloodstain.

151
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,250
This is physical evidence.

152
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,960
He can't deny his involvement.

153
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,420
We'll know once we test it.

154
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,740
Do you really think it was him?

155
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,050
Tell me, why does the law

156
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,570
only allow them to hold me for 12 hours?

157
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,040
They said there wasn't enough evidence,

158
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,120
so they let me go.

159
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,640
Do you really wish

160
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,000
they could keep me for 480 hours?

161
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,640
No rush to lock you up.

162
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,280
Thanks.

163
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,300
He won't be cocky for long.

164
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:39,080
The police just asked me about

165
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:41,840
the link between the Jiang family massacre and Xiao Tianman.

166
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,900
They're already investigating him.

167
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,240
Just wait and see.
